name: Hodl Island
description:
Welcome to HODL Island a place
for community, shared optimism
and belief in the power of human
collaboration. Let's celebrate the
future that unites us. We hodl
what we care for. Collaboration
with Ian Worrel. Digital mixed
media: Gravity Sketch(VR),
Quill(VR), Blender, Photoshop,
After Effects
